Oh, I thought you would never come back.

608
00:28:29,080 --> 00:28:30,360
Mom, there's a dispute at the labor union.

609
00:28:30,400 --> 00:28:31,240
Go and take a look.

610
00:28:33,800 --> 00:28:35,280
Let the union handle it.

611
00:28:35,400 --> 00:28:36,440
