613
00:28:37,720 --> 00:28:39,040
Look, I'm back.

614
00:28:39,040 --> 00:28:40,260
Mom, I'll go with you, okay?

615
00:28:40,260 --> 00:28:41,160
Don't bother me.

616
00:28:41,160 --> 00:28:42,280
