650
00:29:49,690 --> 00:29:51,510
I can't ignore Li Guangnan's situation.

651
00:29:53,120 --> 00:29:54,640
I hope you can understand.

652
00:29:55,840 --> 00:29:57,640
I know you have a lot of people
in your world,

653
