668
00:31:46,000 --> 00:31:47,160
- No.
- Exactly.

669
00:31:47,160 --> 00:31:48,160
I always let you have your way.

670
00:31:48,960 --> 00:31:51,240
That's because you are always right.

671
00:31:51,760 --> 00:31:52,880
Exactly,

672
00:31:52,880 --> 00:31:54,440
I have always been right.

673
00:31:55,000 --> 00:31:57,200
When two people are right for each other,
everything is harmonious.

674
00:31:57,440 --> 00:31:58,480
- Isn't that true?
- Absolutely.

675
00:31:58,480 --> 00:32:00,240
If two people aren't harmonious,

676
00:32:00,240 --> 00:32:01,360
how can there be

677
00:32:01,480 --> 00:32:03,160
eternity,

678
00:32:03,760 --> 00:32:06,480
