680
00:32:10,440 --> 00:32:11,280
Isn't that right?

681
00:32:11,670 --> 00:32:12,560
Absolutely, all correct.

682
00:32:12,560 --> 00:32:15,160
So, if they are not harmonious,

683
00:32:15,160 --> 00:32:17,280
