00:38:06,120 --> 00:38:07,440
I have works by Wang Shuo, Mo Yan,

798
00:38:07,440 --> 00:38:08,280
Wang Xiaobo, everything.

799
00:38:08,520 --> 00:38:09,680
Do you have any books by Su Tong?

800
00:38:09,680 --> 00:38:11,240
I love reading his books.

801
00:38:11,240 --> 00:38:12,240
Of course I do.

802
00:38:13,280 --> 00:38:15,360
Then I'll benefit from it.

803
00:38:17,840 --> 00:38:19,520
Are you hungry? Let's order.

804
00:38:19,520 --> 00:38:20,520
- Okay.
- Okay.

