808
00:38:26,120 --> 00:38:27,040
You go ahead.

809
00:38:28,120 --> 00:38:30,840
Their salami is highly recommended.

810
00:38:30,840 --> 00:38:33,600
But I heard that German-style salami

811
00:38:33,600 --> 00:38:35,200
